{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6a8d6b0ec8","title":"给军委常委的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"21a6508c87","index":0,"year":1966,"month":3,"day":22,"articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"陈毅","id":"1feb996ca7","type":"人物"},{"name":"书信","id":"2a70b5d939","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"文学艺术","id":"5387dec24b","type":"主题"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"林彪","id":"cce608ea44","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","name":"红旗一九六七年第九期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"《红旗》杂志编辑部","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"f326d8be5e","name":"林彪"}]},"publication_details":{"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3ec63011d5","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪同志给中央重委常委的信","index":0,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1f727a5f49","type":"paragraph","text":"常卖请同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fbb3891120","type":"paragraph","text":"送去江青同志召开的部队文艺工作座读会纪要，精阅。这个纪要，经过参加座该会的同志何反复研究，又经过主席三次亲自审阅修改，是一个很好的文件，用毛泽东思想回答了社会主义时期文化革命的许多重大周题，不仅有极大的现实意义而直有深远的历史意义","index":2,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf47bd2a6a","type":"paragraph","text":"十六年来，文艺战上存在着失锐的阶级斗章，战胜推的周题还没有解决。文艺这个弹地，无产阶级不去占领，黄产阶级就必然去占领，十等是不可避免的。这是在意藏形态领域里极为广泛、深刻的社会主义革命，搞不好就会出修正主义。我们达须高举毛泽系思想伟大红旗，坚定不移地把这一号羊命进行到底。","index":3,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"66efdbff8c","type":"paragraph","text":"纪要中提出的周题和意见，完全符合部队文艺工作的实际情况，必须坚决贯彻执行，使部队文艺工作在突出政治、促进人的革命化方面起重要作用。","index":4,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d3ff5cd11f","type":"paragraph","text":"对纪要有何意见整告，以便报中央审批。","index":5,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"81b9d4cc7f","type":"paragraph","text":"此致敬礼！","index":6,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2e7a115d43","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪","index":7,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"21f38d05c8","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年三月二十二日","index":8,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":12,"end":12}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"07ab588da3","type":"paragraph","text":"对纪要有何意见望告，以便报中央审批。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"081316286f","type":"paragraph","text":"纪要中提出的问题和意见，完全符合部队文艺工作的实际情况，必须坚决贯彻执行，使部队文艺工作在突出政治，促使人的革命化方面起重要作用。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4b92824971","type":"paragraph","text":"此致","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5eceed4f10","type":"paragraph","text":"刊载于《高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗》（林彪文集），1967年4月编印，编印者不明。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"61929db86b","type":"paragraph","text":"十六年来，文艺战线上存在着尖锐的阶级斗争，谁战胜谁的问题还没有解决。文艺这个阵地，无产阶级不去占领，资产阶级就必然去占领，斗争是不可避免的。这是在意识形态领域里极为广泛、深刻的社会主义革命，搞不好就会出修正主义。我们必须高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗，坚定不移地把这一场革命进行到底。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9593166590","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年三月二十二日","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9d8103016b","type":"paragraph","text":"送去江青同志三月九日的信和她召开的部队文艺工作座谈会纪要，请阅。这个纪要，经过参加座谈会的同志们反复研究，又经过主席三次亲自审阅和修改，是一个很好的文件，用毛泽东思想回答了社会主义时期文化革命的许多重大问题，不仅有极大的现实意义，而且有深远的历史意义。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a5c663a258","type":"paragraph","text":"常委诸同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"af945d1a8a","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c7e6b6cba4","type":"paragraph","text":"敬礼！","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf51efe549","type":"paragraph","text":"编者注：另据另一本林彪文集（无封面，无封底，编印者及编辑时间不明），此信开头不是“常委诸同志：”，而是“××、荣臻、陈毅、伯承、向前、剑英诸同志：”，此处“××”应是文集编者回避某一个人的名字。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d820f8b9f4","type":"title","text":"给军委常委的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}